'''哈薛'''（{{lang-en|Hazael}}, {{IPAc-en|ˈ|h|eɪ|z|i|əl}}；{{Hebrew name|חֲזָהאֵל|Ḥaza'ēl|H̱azā'ēl}}；<ref>I Kings 19:15</ref>{{lang-arc|חזאל}}，他的名字意为, "上帝看见了"；{{lang-akk|𒄩𒍝𒀪𒀭|Ḫa-za-’-[[丁吉爾|ilu]]}}）原来为大臣，后来成为亚兰国王，被圣经提及。<ref name="Hastingp832">{{cite book|title=A dictionary of the Bible: dealing with its language, literature, and contents, including the Biblical theology, Volume 3|last2=Driver|first2=Samuel Rolles|publisher=T. & T. Clark|year=1899|page=832|first1=James|last1=Hastings}}</ref><ref name="Arnoldp46">{{cite book|title=Dictionary of the Old Testament: historical books|last2=Williamson|first2=Hugh Godfrey Maturin|publisher=InterVarsity Press|year=2006|edition=Illustrated|page=46|first1=Bill T.|last1=Arnold|ISBN=978-0-8308-1782-5}}</ref> 在他的统治下，[[亞蘭大馬士革|亚兰大马士革]] 扩张成为一个疆域涵盖大部分叙利亚和以色列的帝国。<ref name="FreedmanMyers2000">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qRtUqxkB7wkC&pg=PA84|title=Eerdmans Dictionary of the Bible|date=31 December 2000|publisher=Amsterdam University Press|isbn=978-90-5356-503-2|page=84|author1=David Noel Freedman|author2=Allen C. Myers|access-date=2017-03-02|archive-date=2017-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170214144011/https://books.google.com/books?id=qRtUqxkB7wkC&pg=PA84|dead-url=no}}</ref>
