== 但遗址石碑（Tel Dan Stele） ==
[[但丘石碑|但遗址石碑]] 被大多数学者认为是哈薛王在打败以色列和犹大国王后树立的。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://theosophical.wordpress.com/2011/07/15/biblical-archaeology-4-the-moabite-stone-a-k-a-mesha-stele/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-03-02 |archive-date=2020-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200111145432/https://theosophical.wordpress.com/2011/07/15/biblical-archaeology-4-the-moabite-stone-a-k-a-mesha-stele/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.biblicalarchaeology.org/daily/biblical-artifacts/artifacts-and-the-bible/the-tel-dan-inscription-the-first-historical-evidence-of-the-king-david-bible-story/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-03-02 |archive-date=2017-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170218124002/http://www.biblicalarchaeology.org/daily/biblical-artifacts/artifacts-and-the-bible/the-tel-dan-inscription-the-first-historical-evidence-of-the-king-david-bible-story/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 最近在es-Safi/[[迦特|迦特]] 的考古发掘发现了哈薛围攻和征服迦特的大量证据。 Telll Zeitah 在公元前九世纪被毁也可能是哈薛军事征服的结果。犹大国王[[約阿施_(猶大)|约阿施]] 抢在哈薛入侵之前将王宫和圣殿的大量财物上贡哈薛，避免了被攻打。
